(1.1 Is the seed where mnemonic phrases come from?) Tj
T*
(No.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Current implementation flow is:) Tj
T*
(- entropy is generated first \(generate_mnemonic -> secrets.token_bytes\(...\)\).) Tj
T*
(- mnemonic words are encoded from entropy + checksum \(entropy_to_mnemonic\).) Tj
T*
(- seed is then derived from mnemonic + optional passphrase \(derive_seed, PBKDF2-HMAC-SHA3-512\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(So mnemonic does not come from seed in this code path. Seed comes from mnemonic.) Tj
